 Configuration EmbeddedCacheManager.getDefaultConfiguration()
          Deprecated. Use EmbeddedCacheManager.getDefaultCacheConfiguration() instead. Please note that before this method was deprecated, modifications on the Configuration returned would be applied to the default cache if it was not started. Since the deprecation, this method returns a copy and so any changes to the returned object won't have any impact on the default cache instance.
